00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.000
Let's say we have two objects, a one-kilogram and a two-kilogram mass.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:47.000
If this falls with a certain speed S1, this one will follow the speed S2.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:51.000
The way we can use this proportionality relationship to a make calculation

